claim.claim-text:
A method implemented in a computing infrastructure (10), comprising:
initiating (600) a user session with a remote server (12);
the remote server (12) allocating (605) for said user session a user ID for the initiating user (60) and a group ID for one or more additional users selectable by the initiating user;
the initiating user (60) selecting (610) content for supply to the initiating user and to the one or more additional users;
the remote server (12) causing the content to be stored in a control repository (22A, 22B);
the remote server (12) controlling supply of the content according to the allocated ID such that all users can share the content under the group ID but only the initiating user can change the content under the user ID;
the sharing (625) of content occurring on different computing devices (60), amongst the initiating user and the one or more additional users; and
communicating amongst the initiating user and the one or more additional users while at the same time sharing the content.
